rating
Discworld concepts help
rating

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Each guild has a top ten table of its members and there is also
a table for all players.  These tables rank players according to
their ratings, a quantity which reflects their prowess in their
respective guild.

The rating is calculated in mysterious ways, taking into account
bonuses, ability to solve quests and age, among other things.

